Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.22,0:01:40.74,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,How do you lose your map at a time like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.79,0:01:44.29,Default,Jaune,0,0,0,,Believe me, I’ve asked myself the same thing ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:50.70,Default,Nora,0,0,0,,Hey, but you made up for it, Mister Muscles!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.70,0:01:54.14,Default,Nora,0,0,0,,You shoulda seen this guy take a giant Grimm head on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:56.81,Default,Jaune,0,0,0,,I couldn’t have done it without Ruby wearing it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:01:58.12,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,Uh, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:01.67,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,Did you see Ren during that fight? He was out of control!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.26,0:02:05.78,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,I’m sorry, I may have lost my temper momentarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.78,0:02:08.26,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,No, no! Out of control as in “awesome”!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.63,0:02:09.79,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,Oooohhh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:12.27,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:17.39,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,{\i1}You did not!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.88,0:02:18.50,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.63,0:02:20.31,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,Right in the middle of the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.44,0:02:23.08,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,Please tell me you let that lady have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.09,0:02:24.22,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:26.88,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,Even if I did really want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:29.86,Default,Nora,0,0,0,,No way, I don’t believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:43.15,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,It’s not a replacement for the real thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:46.10,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,but I’ll make sure to make good use of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:47.75,Default,Jaune,0,0,0,,That’s amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.37,0:02:49.46,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.24,0:02:53.96,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,And it’s just as strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:56.25,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,Sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:00.78,Default,Nora,0,0,0,,Wanna bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:03.93,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,Nora, please, now’s not the time…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:09.47,Default,Jaune,0,0,0,,– Don’t let her beat you! You can do it! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:09.47,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,– You can do this! Show ‘em what Team JNPR’s made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:12.89,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,C’mon, sis! Aw, you can’t lose to a girl in a skirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:14.89,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,You wear a skirt, Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:17.30,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,Weiss, you’re not cheering loud enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.62,0:03:22.14,Default,Nora,0,0,0,,It definitely feels like the original, I’ll give you that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:23.34,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:26.22,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,But, it does have some new features!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:28.64,Default,Nora,0,0,0,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:35.47,Default,Jaune,0,0,0,,Did she…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:36.49,Default,Jaune,0,0,0,,...win?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:48.43,Default,Jaune,0,0,0,,{\i1}We ate it all…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:50.94,Default,Jaune,0,0,0,,I think I’m gonna be sick…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:53.58,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,Easy there, Vomit Boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:54.94,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:58.01,Default,Jaune,0,0,0,,Oh, we’re doing nickname throwbacks now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:03:59.67,Default,Jaune,0,0,0,,Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:04.20,Default,Nora,0,0,0,,I mean, the Ice Queen seems to like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:10.09,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,I so did not miss you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:14.25,Default,Nora,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh, she really does like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:17.80,Default,Nora,0,0,0,,What went and warmed your heart while you were gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:18.62,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:21.02,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,You make it sound like I used to be terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:22.22,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:24.22,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,Just a lot to deal with it once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:28.60,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,It’s been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:30.83,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,We’ve all grown in our own ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:32.89,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,You really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:35.94,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,Well, think back to when we were all at Beacon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:38.75,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,would you say you ever did anything foolish or embarrassing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:41.02,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,Or do you think you were perfect?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:43.26,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,Oh gosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:47.30,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,I may have been a little too gung-ho from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.21,0:04:49.08,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:52.34,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,I tried to 1v1 a Nevermore on the second day of school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:53.83,Default,Jaune,0,0,0,,Yeah, well…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:55.83,Default,Jaune,0,0,0,,...don’t even get me started.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:04:58.53,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,Well that embarrassment –
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:02.14,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,that desire to go back and tell yourself not to be so stupid –
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:05.14,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,that just proves you’re not the same person you used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:07.26,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,You’re smarter,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:08.51,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,you’re kinder,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:09.60,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,you’re stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:12.30,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,and you’re not done growing yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:13.67,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,None of us are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:19.84,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,Yeah, turns out Ren gets real deep when he feels like talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:22.92,Default,Nora,0,0,0,,Well, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:25.48,Default,Nora,0,0,0,,I thought I was pretty great in school!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:29.43,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,Even at the dance? When you spilled punch all over yourself in front of-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:31.89,Default,Nora,0,0,0,,Yes, especially the dance! Thank you, Yang!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:37.62,Default,Qrow,0,0,0,,{\i1}How can six kids possibly make so much noise eating dinner?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:00.90,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,So, the Maidens...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:02.13,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.31,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,Salem...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:04.72,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,It’s all true?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:06.36,Default,Qrow,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:08.15,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Miss Xiao Long,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:10.95,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,is this more or less what your mother told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.80,0:06:15.13,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,For the most part.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:17.13,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,You forgot something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:21.57,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,You forgot to tell everyone what you did to Qrow and my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:26.00,Default,Jaune,0,0,0,,What is she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:28.00,Default,Qrow,0,0,0,,Oh, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:33.42,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,That’s not a secret I thought she would give up so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:36.77,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Your mother must trust you a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:43.66,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,My ability to reincarnate, though a curse,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:46.07,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,isn’t without a few key benefits.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:50.58,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Much like the Maidens, I too possess a certain…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:52.07,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,...magical power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:59.92,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Using this power, I was able to gift the Branwen twins the ability to see more,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:03.39,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,to move freely and be unburdened by their natural bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:04.59,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:06.28,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:09.94,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,...gave them the ability to turn into birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.27,0:07:14.79,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Rather ridiculous sounding out loud, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:16.34,Default,Oscar,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, what?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:19.03,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:22.28,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,You turned them… into birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.64,0:07:23.39,Default,Nora,0,0,0,,Alright,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.39,0:07:25.77,Default,Nora,0,0,0,,now you’re just messing with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:27.02,Default,Jaune,0,0,0,,What else is new?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:28.70,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,{\i1}He’s telling the truth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:30.70,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,We saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:32.57,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,Yang’s mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:34.01,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,...changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:35.63,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,...right in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:42.24,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,Why would you do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:44.06,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,I mean, what is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:45.86,Default,Qrow,0,0,0,,Yang, that’s enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.64,0:07:48.00,Default,Qrow,0,0,0,,We made a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.39,0:07:49.52,Default,Qrow,0,0,0,,We wanted this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:53.12,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:08:00.26,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,{\i1}Granting this power to them was no trivial task,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:03.48,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,and I can assure you it was not done frivolously.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:08.26,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,I required assistance in gathering information on Salem’s plans,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:11.77,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,as well as searching for Maidens when their hosts became unclear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.00,0:08:16.22,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,Okay, so, have you done this with others?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:19.34,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,Like General Ironwood? Or Professor Goodwitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:22.09,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,As helpful as that might be,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.38,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,unfortunately it is not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.57,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,My power is finite,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:28.57,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,and if I’m being honest, dwindling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:33.19,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,The amount that I gifted to Qrow and Raven was, all things considered,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.52,0:08:34.64,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,rather miniscule.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,0:08:38.62,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,You see, centuries ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.80,0:08:42.20,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,I sacrificed a great deal of magic to four young women,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:45.08,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,who I hoped would use my gift for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:47.12,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,They
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.12,0:08:48.63,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,were the first Maidens
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:56.24,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Miss Xiao Long, it was never my intention to lie to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:08:58.06,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,To any of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:01.26,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,There are just some matters that I prefer to…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.99,0:09:03.68,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,…play close to the chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.05,0:09:05.88,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,I believe that’s how you phrased it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.64,0:09:08.41,Default,Qrow,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:11.14,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Everyone has a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.64,0:09:14.24,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,The Branwens chose to accept their powers
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:16.68,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,and the responsibilities that came with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:18.68,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,And later,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:23.38,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,one of them chose to abandon her duties in favor of her own self-interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:27.06,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Now, all of you have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:32.08,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,If anyone wishes to leave, now is the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:35.90,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,There’s no shame or disgrace in abstaining,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.57,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,only in retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:46.34,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Very well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:50.34,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,Yang?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.79,0:09:53.23,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,If Ruby sticks around,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:54.25,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,then I will too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.18,0:09:59.22,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,If there’s one thing I know about her, it’s that she somehow always knows the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:03.70,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:05.16,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,if we’re going to help,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:07.43,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,if we’re going to keep risking our lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.45,0:10:09.66,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,no more lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:11.54,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,No more half-truths.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:21.60,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:29.06,Default,Jaune,0,0,0,,So… what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:31.41,Default,Jaune,0,0,0,,I mean, what can we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:35.71,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,That is a difficult question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:39.01,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,One that I believe is best answered tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:41.16,Default,Jaune,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.81,0:10:45.64,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,The road ahead is undoubtedly filled with hardships and peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.12,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:49.94,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,it’s been far too long since you have all been together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.84,0:10:52.50,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Please, take tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:54.30,Default,Ozpin,0,0,0,,enjoy this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:05.10,Default,Nora,0,0,0,,Raven?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:06.35,Default,Nora,0,0,0,,Qrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:09.68,Default,Nora,0,0,0,,They’re birds!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.47,0:11:11.51,Default,Nora,0,0,0,,Cracked it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:17.94,Default,Mercury,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey ugly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.22,0:11:29.10,Default,Mercury,0,0,0,,Is Raven Branwen home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:35.76,Default,Shay,0,0,0,,Ya know, I’ve had a real bad week.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:38.68,Default,Shay,0,0,0,,So I think I’m gonna take it out on you-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:47.34,Default,Mercury,0,0,0,,Doesn’t look like he wants to cooperate, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.76,0:11:51.19,Default,Cinder,0,0,0,,Then make him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:54.58,Default,Mercury,0,0,0,,I was hoping you’d say that.
